            "title": "WSL Ubuntu 美化",
            "date_published": "2023-01-23T12:57:23.000Z",
            "content_html": "<p>自从微软公布了WSL后我就玩得不亦乐乎，重装系统后配置好的终端美化没了。很多步骤的忘了，记个笔记以备以后不备之需。</p>\n<p><strong>环境</strong></p>\n<p>系统：Windows 11</p>\n<p>版本：Cumulative Update for Windows 11 Insider Preview (10.0.22623.1180) (KB5022363)</p>\n<p><strong>子系统：Ubuntu</strong></p>\n<p><strong>子系统版本：22.04.1 LTS</strong></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"1-安装WSL\"><a href=\"#1-安装WSL\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.安装WSL\"></a>1.安装WSL</h2><p>微软官网上写得很清楚：<a href=\"https://learn.microsoft.com/zh-cn/windows/wsl/install\">安装 WSL | Microsoft Learn</a></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"2-安装zsh\"><a href=\"#2-安装zsh\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.安装zsh\"></a>2.安装zsh</h2><p>Linux系统有许多中终端(shell)类型。除了默认的<code>bash</code>之外，还有<code>sh</code>，<code>ash</code>，<code>ksh</code>，<code>csh</code>，以及<code>zsh</code>。</p>\n<p>其中<code>zsh</code>在shell当中美化非常漂亮，个人很喜欢。</p>\n<h3 id=\"检查是否已安装shell\"><a href=\"#检查是否已安装shell\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"检查是否已安装shell\"></a>检查是否已安装shell</h3><p>终端输入：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs bash\"><span class=\"hljs-built_in\">cat</span> /etc/shells<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>以查看系统中已安装的shell</p>\n<details>\n    <summary>我的输出</summary>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs shell\">lkhsss@LKH-PC:~$ cat /etc/shells<br><span class=\"hljs-meta prompt_\"># </span><span class=\"language-bash\">/etc/shells: valid login shells</span><br>/bin/sh<br>/bin/bash<br>/usr/bin/bash<br>/bin/rbash<br>/usr/bin/rbash<br>/usr/bin/sh<br>/bin/dash<br>/usr/bin/dash<br>/usr/bin/tmux<br>/usr/bin/screen<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</details>\n\n<p>如果显示结果中包含<code>zsh</code>，可以直接跳到配置zsh</p>\n<h3 id=\"安装zsh\"><a href=\"#安装zsh\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装zsh\"></a>安装zsh</h3><p>终端输入:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs bash\">apt install zsh<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<details>\n    <summary>我的输出</summary>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs shell\">lkhsss@LKH-PC:~$ sudo apt install zsh<br>Reading package lists... Done<br>Building dependency tree... Done<br>Reading state information... Done<br>Suggested packages:<br>  zsh-doc<br>The following NEW packages will be installed:<br>  zsh<br>0 upgraded, 1 newly installed, 0 to remove and 0 not upgraded.<br>Need to get 707 kB of archives.<br>After this operation, 2390 kB of additional disk space will be used.<br>Get:1 http://mirrors.aliyun.com/ubuntu focal-security/main amd64 zsh amd64 5.8-3ubuntu1.1 [707 kB]<br>Fetched 707 kB in 1s (1365 kB/s)<br>Selecting previously unselected package zsh.<br>(Reading database ... 27850 files and directories currently installed.)<br>Preparing to unpack .../zsh_5.8-3ubuntu1.1_amd64.deb ...<br>Unpacking zsh (5.8-3ubuntu1.1) ...<br>Setting up zsh (5.8-3ubuntu1.1) ...<br>Processing triggers for man-db (2.10.2-1) ...<br>lkhsss@LKH-PC:~$<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</details>\n\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"3-配置zsh\"><a href=\"#3-配置zsh\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3.配置zsh\"></a>3.配置zsh</h2><h3 id=\"安装Oh-My-Zsh\"><a href=\"#安装Oh-My-Zsh\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装Oh-My-Zsh\"></a>安装Oh-My-Zsh</h3><p>可选自动安装或者手动安装</p>\n<h4 id=\"自动安装Oh-My-Zsh\"><a href=\"#自动安装Oh-My-Zsh\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"自动安装Oh-My-Zsh\"></a>自动安装Oh-My-Zsh</h4><p>因为zsh配置很多，很多人不能自行把自己的shell美化（甚至会变丑，比如我），所以我选择使用网上别人配置好的文件。</p>\n<p>此次我选择了<a href=\"https://ohmyz.sh/\"><strong>Oh My Zsh</strong></a>，因为它可以换主题。Github：<a href=\"https://github.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh\">ohmyzsh</a></p>\n<p>输入：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs bash\">sh -c <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;<span class=\"hljs-subst\">$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh/master/tools/install.sh)</span>&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>如出现<code>curl: (6) Could not resolve host: raw.githubusercontent.com</code>的问题，这说明无法连接github（WSL网络和windows隔离）。如果不想折腾hosts或者代理，那么可以选择<a href=\"#%E6%89%8B%E5%8A%A8%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85Oh-My-Zsh\">手动安装</a>。</p>\n<h4 id=\"手动安装Oh-My-Zsh\"><a href=\"#手动安装Oh-My-Zsh\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"手动安装Oh-My-Zsh\"></a>手动安装Oh-My-Zsh</h4><p>用gitee镜像源克隆oh-my-zsh</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs bash\">git <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">clone</span> https://gitee.com/mirrors/oh-my-zsh.git ~/.oh-my-zsh<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<details>\n    <summary>输出</summary>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs shell\">lkhsss@LKH-PC:~$ git clone https://gitee.com/mirrors/oh-my-zsh.git ~/.oh-my-zsh<br>Cloning into &#x27;/home/lkhsss/.oh-my-zsh&#x27;...<br>remote: Enumerating objects: 30309, done.<br>remote: Counting objects: 100% (30309/30309), done.<br>remote: Compressing objects: 100% (11786/11786), done.<br>remote: Total 30309 (delta 17822), reused 29356 (delta 17296), pack-reused 0<br>Receiving objects: 100% (30309/30309), 6.26 MiB | 951.00 KiB/s, done.<br>Resolving deltas: 100% (17822/17822), done.<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</details>\n\n<p>然后复制ohmyzsh配置文件到zsh配置文件</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs bash\"><span class=\"hljs-built_in\">cp</span> ~/.oh-my-zsh/templates/zshrc.zsh-template ~/.zshrc<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"安装powerlevel10k主题\"><a href=\"#安装powerlevel10k主题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装powerlevel10k主题\"></a>安装powerlevel10k主题</h3><p>官方源安装：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs bash\">git <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">clone</span> --depth=1 https://github.com/romkatv/powerlevel10k.git <span class=\"hljs-variable\">$&#123;ZSH_CUSTOM:-<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$HOME</span>/.oh-my-zsh/custom&#125;</span>/themes/powerlevel10k<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>国内镜像源安装：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs bash\">git <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">clone</span> --depth=1 https://gitee.com/romkatv/powerlevel10k.git <span class=\"hljs-variable\">$&#123;ZSH_CUSTOM:-<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$HOME</span>/.oh-my-zsh/custom&#125;</span>/themes/powerlevel10k<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"配置主题为p10k\"><a href=\"#配置主题为p10k\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"配置主题为p10k\"></a>配置主题为p10k</h3><p>打开<code>~/.zshrc</code>文件</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs bash\">vim ~/.zshrc<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>找到<code>ZSH_THEME=&quot;robbyrussell&quot;</code>这一行，把它注释掉。</p>\n<p>在这句后面补上<code>ZSH_THEME=&quot;powerlevel10k/powerlevel10k&quot;</code></p>\n<p>即为</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs bash\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\"># ZSH_THEME=&quot;robbyrussell&quot;</span><br>ZSH_THEME=<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;powerlevel10k/powerlevel10k&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"配置powerlevel10k主题\"><a href=\"#配置powerlevel10k主题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"配置powerlevel10k主题\"></a>配置powerlevel10k主题</h3><p>再修改完<code>~/.zshrc</code>文件后，终端输入<code>source ~/.zshrc</code>即可生效</p>\n<p>如果安装和配置成功，powerlevel10k会显示配置画面</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Lkhsss/picx@main/Linux/WSL/WSL-Ubuntu-%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEpowerlevel10k%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98.webp\" alt=\"配置powerlevel10k主题\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"详细配置\"><a href=\"#详细配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"详细配置\"></a>详细配置</h4><p>这个图案像一个钻石吗（菱形）？</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Lkhsss/picx@main/Linux/WSL/WSL-Ubuntu-%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/%E8%BF%99%E4%B8%AA%E5%9B%BE%E6%A1%88%E5%83%8F%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E8%8F%B1%E5%BD%A2%E5%90%97.webp\" alt=\"这个图案像一个菱形吗\"></p>\n<p>这个图案像一个锁吗？</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Lkhsss/picx@main/Linux/WSL/WSL-Ubuntu-%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/%E8%BF%99%E4%B8%AA%E5%9B%BE%E6%A1%88%E5%83%8F%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E9%94%81%E5%90%97.webp\" alt=\"这个图案像一个锁吗\"></p>\n<p>这个图案像Linux Debian系列的logo吗？</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Lkhsss/picx@main/Linux/WSL/WSL-Ubuntu-%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/%E8%BF%99%E4%B8%AA%E5%9B%BE%E6%A1%88%E5%83%8FLinux-Debian%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97%E7%9A%84logo%E5%90%97.webp\" alt=\"这个图案像Linux-Debian系列的logo吗\"></p>\n<p>这些小图标是否和字符没有重合？</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Lkhsss/picx@main/Linux/WSL/WSL-Ubuntu-%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/%E8%BF%99%E4%BA%9B%E5%B0%8F%E5%9B%BE%E6%A0%87%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E5%92%8C%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E9%87%8D%E5%90%88.webp\" alt=\"这些小图标是否和字符没有重合\"></p>\n<p>提示符样式</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Lkhsss/picx@main/Linux/WSL/WSL-Ubuntu-%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA%E7%AC%A6%E6%A0%B7%E5%BC%8F.webp\" alt=\"提示符样式\"></p>\n<p>提示符外框形状</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Lkhsss/picx@main/Linux/WSL/WSL-Ubuntu-%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA%E7%AC%A6%E5%A4%96%E6%A1%86%E5%BD%A2%E7%8A%B6.webp\" alt=\"提示符外框形状\"></p>\n<p>是否显示实时时间</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Lkhsss/picx@main/Linux/WSL/WSL-Ubuntu-%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/image.webp\" alt=\"image\"></p>\n<p>提示符外框分隔形状</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Lkhsss/picx@main/Linux/WSL/WSL-Ubuntu-%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA%E7%AC%A6%E5%A4%96%E6%A1%86%E5%88%86%E9%9A%94%E5%BD%A2%E7%8A%B6.webp\" alt=\"提示符外框分隔形状\"></p>\n<p>提示符外框图形顶端样式</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Lkhsss/picx@main/Linux/WSL/WSL-Ubuntu-%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA%E7%AC%A6%E5%A4%96%E6%A1%86%E5%9B%BE%E5%BD%A2%E9%A1%B6%E7%AB%AF%E6%A0%B7%E5%BC%8F.webp\" alt=\"提示符外框图形顶端样式\"></p>\n<p>提示符外框图形尾部样式</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Lkhsss/picx@main/Linux/WSL/WSL-Ubuntu-%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA%E7%AC%A6%E5%A4%96%E6%A1%86%E5%9B%BE%E5%BD%A2%E9%A1%B6%E7%AB%AF%E6%A0%B7%E5%BC%8F.webp\" alt=\"提示符外框图形顶端样式\"></p>\n<p>提示符是否换行</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Lkhsss/picx@main/Linux/WSL/WSL-Ubuntu-%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA%E7%AC%A6%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E6%8D%A2%E8%A1%8C.webp\" alt=\"提示符输入是否换行\"></p>\n<p>提示符首端末端连接样式</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Lkhsss/picx@main/Linux/WSL/WSL-Ubuntu-%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA%E7%AC%A6%E9%A6%96%E7%AB%AF%E6%9C%AB%E7%AB%AF%E8%BF%9E%E6%8E%A5%E6%A0%B7%E5%BC%8F.webp\" alt=\"提示符首端末端连接样式\"></p>\n<p>提示符整体框架样式</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Lkhsss/picx@main/Linux/WSL/WSL-Ubuntu-%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA%E7%AC%A6%E6%95%B4%E4%BD%93%E6%A1%86%E6%9E%B6%E6%A0%B7%E5%BC%8F.webp\" alt=\"提示符整体框架样式\"></p>\n<p>框架颜色</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Lkhsss/picx@main/Linux/WSL/WSL-Ubuntu-%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/%E6%A1%86%E6%9E%B6%E9%A2%9C%E8%89%B2.webp\" alt=\"框架颜色\"></p>\n<p>提示符之间距离</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Lkhsss/picx@main/Linux/WSL/WSL-Ubuntu-%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA%E7%AC%A6%E4%B9%8B%E9%97%B4%E8%B7%9D%E7%A6%BB.webp\" alt=\"提示符之间距离\"></p>\n<p>是否显示小图标</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Lkhsss/picx@main/Linux/WSL/WSL-Ubuntu-%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E5%B0%8F%E5%9B%BE%E6%A0%87.webp\" alt=\"是否显示小图标\"></p>\n<p>显示文字提示</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Lkhsss/picx@main/Linux/WSL/WSL-Ubuntu-%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E6%96%87%E5%AD%97%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA.webp\" alt=\"显示文字提示\"></p>\n<p>瞬时提示</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Lkhsss/picx@main/Linux/WSL/WSL-Ubuntu-%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/%E7%9E%AC%E6%97%B6%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA.webp\" alt=\"瞬时提示\"></p>\n<p>即时提示模式（不知道啥玩意，听说开了可能会出错）</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Lkhsss/picx@main/Linux/WSL/WSL-Ubuntu-%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/%E5%8D%B3%E6%97%B6%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F.webp\" alt=\"即时提示模式\"></p>\n<p>自动将配置保存到配置文件</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Lkhsss/picx@main/Linux/WSL/WSL-Ubuntu-%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E5%B0%86%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E4%BF%9D%E5%AD%98%E5%88%B0%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6.webp\" alt=\"自动将配置保存到配置文件\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"修改小图标\"><a href=\"#修改小图标\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"修改小图标\"></a>修改小图标</h3><p>在<code>~/.p10k.zsh</code>里可以修改一些微小的设置</p>\n<p>这是左边提示符设置</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs bash\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\"># The list of segments shown on the left. Fill it with the most important segments.</span><br><span class=\"hljs-built_in\">typeset</span> -g POWERLEVEL9K_LEFT_PROMPT_ELEMENTS=(<br>  <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># =========================[ Line #1 ]=========================</span><br>  os_icon                 <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># os identifier</span><br>  <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">dir</span>                     <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># current directory</span><br>  vcs                     <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># git status</span><br>  <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># =========================[ Line #2 ]=========================</span><br>  newline                 <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># \\n</span><br>  <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># prompt_char           # prompt symbol</span><br>)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>这是右边提示符设置（我开启了CPU负荷显示和内存剩余）</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br><span class=\"line\">36</span><br><span class=\"line\">37</span><br><span class=\"line\">38</span><br><span class=\"line\">39</span><br><span class=\"line\">40</span><br><span class=\"line\">41</span><br><span class=\"line\">42</span><br><span class=\"line\">43</span><br><span class=\"line\">44</span><br><span class=\"line\">45</span><br><span class=\"line\">46</span><br><span class=\"line\">47</span><br><span class=\"line\">48</span><br><span class=\"line\">49</span><br><span class=\"line\">50</span><br><span class=\"line\">51</span><br><span class=\"line\">52</span><br><span class=\"line\">53</span><br><span class=\"line\">54</span><br><span class=\"line\">55</span><br><span class=\"line\">56</span><br><span class=\"line\">57</span><br><span class=\"line\">58</span><br><span class=\"line\">59</span><br><span class=\"line\">60</span><br><span class=\"line\">61</span><br><span class=\"line\">62</span><br><span class=\"line\">63</span><br><span class=\"line\">64</span><br><span class=\"line\">65</span><br><span class=\"line\">66</span><br><span class=\"line\">67</span><br><span class=\"line\">68</span><br><span class=\"line\">69</span><br><span class=\"line\">70</span><br><span class=\"line\">71</span><br><span class=\"line\">72</span><br><span class=\"line\">73</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs bash\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\"># The list of segments shown on the right. Fill it with less important segments.</span><br>  <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># Right prompt on the last prompt line (where you are typing your commands) gets</span><br>  <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># automatically hidden when the input line reaches it. Right prompt above the</span><br>  <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># last prompt line gets hidden if it would overlap with left prompt.</span><br>  <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">typeset</span> -g POWERLEVEL9K_RIGHT_PROMPT_ELEMENTS=(<br>    <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># =========================[ Line #1 ]=========================</span><br>    status                  <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># exit code of the last command</span><br>    command_execution_time  <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># duration of the last command</span><br>    background_jobs         <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># presence of background jobs</span><br>    direnv                  <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># direnv status (https://direnv.net/)</span><br>    asdf                    <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># asdf version manager (https://github.com/asdf-vm/asdf)</span><br>    virtualenv              <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># python virtual environment (https://docs.python.org/3/library/venv.html)</span><br>    anaconda                <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># conda environment (https://conda.io/)</span><br>    pyenv                   <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># python environment (https://github.com/pyenv/pyenv)</span><br>    goenv                   <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># go environment (https://github.com/syndbg/goenv)</span><br>    nodenv                  <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># node.js version from nodenv (https://github.com/nodenv/nodenv)</span><br>    nvm                     <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># node.js version from nvm (https://github.com/nvm-sh/nvm)</span><br>    nodeenv                 <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># node.js environment (https://github.com/ekalinin/nodeenv)</span><br>    <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># node_version          # node.js version</span><br>    <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># go_version            # go version (https://golang.org)</span><br>    <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># rust_version          # rustc version (https://www.rust-lang.org)</span><br>    <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># dotnet_version        # .NET version (https://dotnet.microsoft.com)</span><br>    <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># php_version           # php version (https://www.php.net/)</span><br>    <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># laravel_version       # laravel php framework version (https://laravel.com/)</span><br>    <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># java_version          # java version (https://www.java.com/)</span><br>    <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># package               # name@version from package.json (https://docs.npmjs.com/files/package.json)</span><br>    rbenv                   <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># ruby version from rbenv (https://github.com/rbenv/rbenv)</span><br>    rvm                     <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># ruby version from rvm (https://rvm.io)</span><br>    fvm                     <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># flutter version management (https://github.com/leoafarias/fvm)</span><br>    luaenv                  <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># lua version from luaenv (https://github.com/cehoffman/luaenv)</span><br>    jenv                    <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># java version from jenv (https://github.com/jenv/jenv)</span><br>    plenv                   <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># perl version from plenv (https://github.com/tokuhirom/plenv)</span><br>    perlbrew                <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># perl version from perlbrew (https://github.com/gugod/App-perlbrew)</span><br>    phpenv                  <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># php version from phpenv (https://github.com/phpenv/phpenv)</span><br>    scalaenv                <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># scala version from scalaenv (https://github.com/scalaenv/scalaenv)</span><br>    haskell_stack           <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># haskell version from stack (https://haskellstack.org/)</span><br>    kubecontext             <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># current kubernetes context (https://kubernetes.io/)</span><br>    terraform               <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># terraform workspace (https://www.terraform.io)</span><br>    <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># terraform_version     # terraform version (https://www.terraform.io)</span><br>    aws                     <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># aws profile (https://docs.aws.amazon.com/cli/latest/userguide/cli-configure-profiles.html)</span><br>    aws_eb_env              <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># aws elastic beanstalk environment (https://aws.amazon.com/elasticbeanstalk/)</span><br>    azure                   <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># azure account name (https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/cli/azure)</span><br>    gcloud                  <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># google cloud cli account and project (https://cloud.google.com/)</span><br>    google_app_cred         <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># google application credentials (https://cloud.google.com/docs/authentication/production)</span><br>    toolbox                 <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># toolbox name (https://github.com/containers/toolbox)</span><br>    context                 <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># user@hostname</span><br>    nordvpn                 <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># nordvpn connection status, linux only (https://nordvpn.com/)</span><br>    ranger                  <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># ranger shell (https://github.com/ranger/ranger)</span><br>    nnn                     <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># nnn shell (https://github.com/jarun/nnn)</span><br>    xplr                    <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># xplr shell (https://github.com/sayanarijit/xplr)</span><br>    vim_shell               <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># vim shell indicator (:sh)</span><br>    midnight_commander      <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># midnight commander shell (https://midnight-commander.org/)</span><br>    nix_shell               <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># nix shell (https://nixos.org/nixos/nix-pills/developing-with-nix-shell.html)</span><br>    vi_mode                 <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># vi mode (you don&#x27;t need this if you&#x27;ve enabled prompt_char)</span><br>    <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># vpn_ip                # virtual private network indicator</span><br>    load                  <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># CPU load</span><br>    <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># disk_usage            # disk usage</span><br>    ram                   <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># free RAM</span><br>    <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># swap                  # used swap</span><br>    todo                    <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># todo items (https://github.com/todotxt/todo.txt-cli)</span><br>    timewarrior             <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># timewarrior tracking status (https://timewarrior.net/)</span><br>    taskwarrior             <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># taskwarrior task count (https://taskwarrior.org/)</span><br>    <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># cpu_arch              # CPU architecture</span><br>    <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># time                  # current time</span><br>    <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># =========================[ Line #2 ]=========================</span><br>    newline<br>    <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># ip                    # ip address and bandwidth usage for a specified network interface</span><br>    <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># public_ip             # public IP address</span><br>    <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># proxy                 # system-wide http/https/ftp proxy</span><br>    <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># battery               # internal battery</span><br>    <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># wifi                  # wifi speed</span><br>    <span class=\"hljs-comment\"># example               # example user-defined segment (see prompt_example function below)</span><br>  )<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"修改用户shell\"><a href=\"#修改用户shell\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"修改用户shell\"></a>修改用户shell</h3><p><code>lkhsss</code>是我的用户名，改成你的就好</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs bash\">chsh -s /bin/zsh lkhsss<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p>如果不加用户名，会把zsh变为默认shell</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"4-安装插件\"><a href=\"#4-安装插件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"4.安装插件\"></a>4.安装插件</h2><h3 id=\"命令语法高亮\"><a href=\"#命令语法高亮\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"命令语法高亮\"></a>命令语法高亮</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs bash\">git <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">clone</span> https://gitee.com/Annihilater/zsh-syntax-highlighting.git <span class=\"hljs-variable\">$&#123;ZSH_CUSTOM:-~/.oh-my-zsh/custom&#125;</span>/plugins/zsh-syntax-highlighting<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"自动命令提示\"><a href=\"#自动命令提示\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"自动命令提示\"></a>自动命令提示</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs bash\">git <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">clone</span> https://github.com/zsh-users/zsh-autosuggestions ~/.oh-my-zsh/plugins/zsh-autosuggestions<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"加载插件\"><a href=\"#加载插件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"加载插件\"></a>加载插件</h3><p>安装好后在<code>~/.zshrc</code>中引入</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs bash\">plugins=(<br>    git<br>    zsh-syntax-highlighting<br>    zsh-autosuggestions<br>)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>最后<code>source ./.zshrc</code>重载</p>\n<h2 id=\"5-安装Neofetch\"><a href=\"#5-安装Neofetch\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"5.安装Neofetch\"></a>5.安装Neofetch</h2><p><strong>Neofetch</strong>，这是一个在终端上显示带有发行徽标的信息的工具。<del>(没卵用but好看</del></p>\n<p>输入</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs bash\">sudo apt install neofetch<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>安装完成后，输入<code>neofetch</code>显示发行版本信息</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Lkhsss/picx@main/Linux/WSL/WSL-Ubuntu-%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/neofetch.webp\" alt=\"neofetch\"></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"最终成品\"><a href=\"#最终成品\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"最终成品\"></a>最终成品</h2><p><img src=\"https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Lkhsss/picx@main/Linux/WSL/WSL-Ubuntu-%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/%E6%9C%80%E7%BB%88%E6%88%90%E5%93%81.webp\" alt=\"最终成品\"></p>\n<p>漂亮吧！嘿嘿嘿嘿</p>\n",
